transcript: The middle of the upper lip formed a sharp wedge and closed firmly on the firm lower one, and something like two distinct smiles played continually round the two corners of the mouth; this, together with the resolute, inso- lent intelligence of his eyes, produced an effect which made it impossible not to notice his face.
